PrecisAppointment of the following Judges as Judges of the Court of Appeal of Nunavut during their tenure of office as Judges of their respective Court, effective April 1, 1999. (The HONOURABLE HARRY C.B. MADDISON, a Judge of the Supreme Court of the Yukon Territory; the HONOURABLE JOHN D. BRACCO, a Judge of the Court of Appeal of Alberta; the HONOURABLE CALVIN F. TALLIS, a Judge of the Court of Appeal for Saskatchewan; the HONOURABLE MARY M. HETHERINGTON, a Judge of the Court of Appeal of Alberta; the HONOURABLE RENÉ P. FOISY, a Judge of the Court of Appeal of Alberta; the HONOURABLE ALLEN B. SULATYCKY, a Judge of the Court of Appeal of Alberta; the HONOURABLE HOWARD L. IRVING, a Judge of the Court of Appeal of Alberta; the HONOURABLE RONALD L. BERGER, a Judge of the Court of Appeal of Alberta; the HONOURABLE JEAN E. CÔTÉ, a Judge of the Court of Appeal of Alberta; the HONOURABLE J. EDWARD RICHARD, a Judge of the Supreme Court of the Northwest Territories; the HONOURABLE JOHN Z. VERTES, a Judge of the Supreme Court of the Northwest Territories; the HONOURABLE CONSTANCE D. HUNT, a Judge of the Court of Appeal of Alberta; the HONOURABLE ANNE H. RUSSELL, a Judge of the Court of Appeal of Alberta; the HONOURABLE RALPH E. HUDSON, a Judge of the Supreme Court of the Yukon Territory; and the HONOURABLE VIRGINIA A. SCHULER, a Judge of the Supreme Court of the Northwest Territories)
